WEBVTT

1
00:19:18.295 --> 00:19:19.986 
晚上好，路易莎。
Good evening, Louisa.

2
00:19:20.020 --> 00:19:21.229 
罗勒。
Basil.

3
00:19:21.263 --> 00:19:22.678 
好吧，你到底在这里干什么？
Well, what the hell are you doing here?

4
00:19:22.713 --> 00:19:24.439 
啊，最后一刻的突发奇想。
Ah, last minute whim.

5
00:19:24.473 --> 00:19:26.406 
从莱切特·明斯特那里跳一跳。
Just a hop and a skip from Lytchett Minster.

6
00:19:26.441 --> 00:19:29.823 
出租车，火车，渡船，火车，
Well, cab, train, ferry, train,

7
00:19:29.858 --> 00:19:33.275 
火车，火车，公共汽车，渡船，
train, train, bus, ferry,

8
00:19:33.310 --> 00:19:34.863 
推车。
cart.

9
00:19:34.897 --> 00:19:37.555 
嗯，我想你最好进来。
Well, I suppose you better come in.

10
00:19:41.766 --> 00:19:44.286 
[行李箱砰砰响]
[suitcase banging]

11
00:19:46.288 --> 00:19:49.671 
你在伦敦见过拉里和亨利·米勒。
You met Larry and Henry Miller in London.

